query.query:
-- query42
SELECT dt.d_year, 
 item.i_category_id, 
 item.i_category, 
 Sum(ss_ext_sales_price) 
FROM date_dim dt, 
 store_sales, 
 item 
WHERE dt.d_date_sk = store_sales.ss_sold_date_sk 
 AND store_sales.ss_item_sk = item.i_item_sk 
 AND item.i_manager_id = 1 
 AND dt.d_moy = 12 
 AND dt.d_year = 2000 
GROUP BY dt.d_year, 
 item.i_category_id, 
 item.i_category 
ORDER BY Sum(ss_ext_sales_price) DESC, 
 dt.d_year, 
 item.i_category_id, 
 item.i_category
LIMIT 100;
